    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1942-04-27T18:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1942-04-27T18:00:00-05:00" n="338"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d338">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">703.5493/13: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Minister in Switzerland</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Harrison</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1942-04-27T19:00:00-04:00"
                            >April 27, 1942—7 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>1066. Department’s 903, April 10. Department’s 444 of even date to the American
                    Legation at Lisbon is quoted below for your information.</p>
                <quote rend="blockquote">
                    <p>“Bona fide American citizens to be repatriated on an exchange vessel may be
                        accompanied by the following: (<hi rend="italic">a</hi>) alien spouses of
                        European or oriental origin, (<hi rend="italic">b</hi>) alien minor
                        children, (<hi rend="italic">c</hi>) alien parents where presence of parent
                        is essential to welfare of children, (<hi rend="italic">d</hi>) alien nurse,
                        companion or servant (except Orientals) accompanying American employer,
                        provided presence certified by physician as necessary.</p>
                    <p>As above persons cannot apply for American visas until they reach neutral
                        country, Portuguese Government should be assured that these categories of
                        aliens will be embarked upon the exchange vessel promptly and will not be
                        permitted to become a burden on the Portuguese Government.”</p>
                </quote>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
